Python makes easy to use date and time function.

date is not a datatype in python.

But date object can be used by using different module like date, time and calendar.

The datetime calsses in python has classsified as six main classes they are.

1) date - It consists of year, month and day.

2) time - It gives out the perfect time by assuming everyday has 24 hrs * 60 min *  60 sec.

3) datetime - It is a grouping of date and time which consist of year, month, day, hour, minute, second, microsecond, and tzinfo.

4) timedelta - It is used difference between two dates, time or datetime instances to microsecond resolution.

5) tzinfo = It is used to return time zion information object.

6) timezone - It is the class that implements the tzinfo abstract base class.

